{"tid":2095302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當局覆檢書籍有否違國安法　書展參展商促盡快交代準則","createTime":"2020-07-05T10:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T10:45:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"256463091e5527beeb39fb63c11c40e99dbdd119","tid":2095302,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:45:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535906-20200705.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535906-20200705.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3zcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=b6e883a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535906-20200705.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=65cd1de8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535906-20200705.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n康文署表示，公共圖書館將覆檢部分書籍的內容會否違反《港區國安法》，有關書籍將暫時不會給予市民借閱或參考用途。<br />\n<br />\n有市民憂慮影響出版自由及下一代選擇，但亦有市民贊成康文署做法，認為國安法是最重要的立法。<br />\n<br />\n書展即將舉行，有參展商表示，當局一日未公布覆檢結果都不會賣有關書籍，希望當局可以盡早交代結果及相關準則。"}]}